title: BRIEF-Wallbridge Enters Into Agreements To Sell 10,870 Ounces Of Gold At CAD$1720
text:
April 4, 2018 / 11:36 AM / Updated 22 minutes ago BRIEF-Wallbridge Enters Into Agreements To Sell 10,870 Ounces Of Gold At CAD$1720 Reuters Staff 
April 4 (Reuters) - Wallbridge Mining Company Ltd: 
* WALLBRIDGE ENTERS INTO AGREEMENTS TO SELL 10,870 OUNCES OF GOLD AT CAD$1720 
* DELIVERIES AND PAYMENTS ARE SCHEDULED BETWEEN AUGUST AND DECEMBER OF 2018
